name: NC Secretary of State
tweet: @cybersupportnet @NASSorg A3(2): Check your corporate records often. For businesses in NC – subscribe for free alerts when your company’s filings are updated. name: NC Secretary of State
tweet: @cybersupportnet @NASSorg A3(1): Keep a keen eye out for social engineering tactics. Phishing attacks will spoof email accounts to gain access to confidential data. Small businesses are the target of 50-75% of ransomware attacks, so remember – cybersecurity is everybody’s business. #BizSchemeSOS

name: NC Secretary of State
tweet: @NASSorg A2: Take care in what you share – innocuous personal information shared on social media can be used by crooks for social engineering purposes. name: NC Secretary of State
tweet: @cybersupportnet @NASSorg A1: Small businesses first need to be aware that they may be targets because they don’t have the anti-fraud resources of a big company.
